EXTRACTED VALUE: "He's gone?" my mother asks, coming quietly through the little side door.
Jack swallowed nervously. The woodland appeared tranquil and safe by daylight, but he knew things could change after dark.
“Do you have a giant net?” I asked him.
"How much did you give to the clinics?"
He hesitated, blew out a quiet breath. "No, sir, Lieutenant, it's not."
A cancelled RGC check had been carefully placed under a paperweight. Fred had probably made a copy to take with him and had left the original here.
